cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a deep learning method for image deconvolution, which is a common problem in computer vision and image processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves training a neural network, which suggests it could be relevant to categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves image processing, which could be relevant to categories such as cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
